    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/d576e47ec29592a74d7f18040459665c_6964230212797294985.png",
                "key": "直率的辭絕",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "直率的辭絕"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">岩元素附魔</span>；從手牌中<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捨棄</span>至多5張<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">裂晶彈片</span>，每<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捨棄</span>1張都使此傷害+1並抽1張牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">岩元素附魔</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>，變為<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/d13eff9275ac9df191b4e1f83bdd18c7_2090368836108021967.png",
                "key": "典儀式晶火",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "典儀式晶火"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>，對所有敵方後臺角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">金花禮炮</span>，生成1張<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">裂晶彈片</span>加入手牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/25547c6b405dc204653b701c121b1096_2223176171615380187.png",
                "key": "如霰澄天的鳴禮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "如霰澄天的鳴禮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">敵方角色受到結晶反應傷害後：</span>生成3張<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">裂晶彈片</span>，隨機置入我方牌庫中。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/7e023ac7d7c52126ccbea78e74621bfd_8498300686110865384.png",
                "key": "互助關係網",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "互助關係網"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p>對敵方「出戰角色」造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>，抽1張牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8062794155777621997.png",
                "key": "裂晶彈片",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/ca5315848113a22db13d032f358ddbdb_4819458860423554051.png",
                "title": "裂晶彈片"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>，抽1張<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">裂晶彈片</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4409448257735787041.png",
                "key": "金花禮炮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/1e170b966fa674e494fba2732677bcd8_7027755953938076066.png",
                "title": "金花禮炮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_9210157504352936852.png",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span></p><p>透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_47878813354392536.png",
